OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers, wintry on the hills, continue
OL,7,Fthrough the evening before clearing
OL,8,Ffrom the east by midnight. This will
OL,9,Fleave the rest of the night dry and
OL,10,Fcold with clear periods.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry and bright but chilly
OL,13,Fstart, becoming cloudy from the
OL,14,Fmorning with outbreaks of heavy rain
OL,15,Fand hill snow from late morning. The
OL,16,Fwind will strengthen towards the
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
