OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,6,Frain, hill snow and gales or severe
OL,7,Fgales clear early Sunday morning,
OL,8,Fleaving a few showers. Mostly dry but
OL,9,Fcloudy Monday and Tuesday with showers
OL,10,Fin west late Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
